# Changelog

## 0.6.0

* Adding `MultiSet`.

## 0.5.0

* Adding `SuffixArray` & `GeneralizedSuffixArray`.
* Better `Trie` sentinel.

## 0.4.0

* Adding `Queue`.
* Adding possibility to pass custom comparator to `Heap` & `FibonacciHeap`.

## 0.3.0

* Adding `FibonacciHeap`.
* Fixing bug related to `Heap`.

## 0.2.0

* Adding `Trie`.

## 0.1.0

* Adding `Heap`.

## 0.0.1

* Adding `LinkedList`.
* Adding `Stack`.
